WEBVTT

00:06.923 --> 00:08.258
- I'm Jan Broberg,

00:08.299 --> 00:11.511
and this series is based
on my story.

00:11.553 --> 00:13.805
I know it may
seem unbelievable,

00:13.847 --> 00:17.726
but we lived in
a different world back then.

00:17.767 --> 00:20.895
I want to tell
my family story today

00:20.937 --> 00:22.397
because so many seem to think

00:22.439 --> 00:25.400
something like this
could never happen to them,

00:25.442 --> 00:29.654
especially at the hands
of someone they know and trust,

00:29.696 --> 00:31.823
but it did happen.

00:31.865 --> 00:36.703
It happened to my family.
It happened to me.

00:36.745 --> 00:39.205
Thank you for watching.

00:45.378 --> 00:48.298
