<i>* *</i>

01:24.084 --> 01:26.044
- Good night, sweetheart.

01:26.086 --> 01:28.630
Everything all right?

01:28.672 --> 01:31.675
- Everything's fine, Mom.
- Okay.

01:31.716 --> 01:33.510
I love you, Jani.

01:51.569 --> 01:53.446
[thump]

01:53.488 --> 01:55.949
