<i>- Today was church,</i>

02:42.162 --> 02:45.331
<i>and we had quite</i>
<i>a good sacrament meeting.</i>

02:45.373 --> 02:47.959
<i>I really had the spirit today.</i>

02:48.001 --> 02:50.837
<i>I'm thankful for</i>
<i>the wonderful parents I have.</i>

02:50.879 --> 02:52.964
<i>My mom and dad</i>
<i>teach me the Gospel</i>

02:53.006 --> 02:54.966
<i>and how to be a good person.</i>

02:55.008 --> 02:56.509
