- She said "hold your horses."

03:10.482 --> 03:11.983
- Who are the Birchers?

03:12.025 --> 03:14.527
- Well, we're gonna
find out today, Freckles.

03:14.569 --> 03:16.279
- Berchtolds, Susan.

03:16.321 --> 03:17.739
Remember,
we met them outside church?

03:17.781 --> 03:20.367
