- Well, what is the Brady Bunch
doing on my lawn?

04:32.022 --> 04:33.648
- That's our favorite show.

04:33.690 --> 04:36.943
- That's no surprise.
You're a dead ringer for Jan.

04:36.985 --> 04:38.236
- I am Jan.

04:38.278 --> 04:39.779
<i>* *</i>

04:39.821 --> 04:41.823
- Well, pleased to meet you,
Jan.

04:41.865 --> 04:45.285
<i>* *</i>

