Brobergs, these are my boy--

05:04.012 --> 05:07.098
boys, boys.

05:07.140 --> 05:09.642
And this is
my lovely wife, Gail.

05:09.684 --> 05:11.436
- Hi there.
<i>- God kveld.</i>

05:11.478 --> 05:13.396
That's Norwegian
