05:13.438 --> 05:15.065
- Huh!

05:15.106 --> 05:17.150
- What's all this?

05:17.192 --> 05:18.443
- Oh.

05:18.485 --> 05:20.862
Well, because we didn't get
to have you over

05:20.904 --> 05:23.823
for a summer picnic,
we decided to move it indoors.

05:23.865 --> 05:27.369
It's a little bit off the wall,
but that's just how we are.

05:27.410 --> 05:29.037
[jaunty piano tune playing]

05:29.079 --> 05:31.915
So, grab a pillow, and I will
grill up some burgers.

05:31.956 --> 05:33.750
Come on in.

05:33.792 --> 05:36.586
The moment I knew
we'd found the perfect place

05:36.628 --> 05:39.464
was when I met you outside
church that day, Mary Ann.

05:39.506 --> 05:41.007
- Oh, goodness.

05:41.049 --> 05:43.927
The girls love growing up here,
and I have no complaints.

05:43.968 --> 05:45.804
- I bet when you were
a little kid,

05:45.845 --> 05:48.682
and you pictured
the perfect place,

05:48.723 --> 05:51.685
