with our own eyes.

08:51.406 --> 08:54.325
- Did the truck start up again?

08:54.367 --> 08:57.245
- No, it never worked right
from that day on.

09:00.832 --> 09:04.085
- You ever seen a thing
like that, Jan?

09:07.922 --> 09:11.676
Well, never say never.

09:15.388 --> 09:20.268
